Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\bord0.5\blur3\fn方正宋三_GBK\fad(150,0)\4a&H64\3c&HFFFFFF&\move(800,300,320,300,0,200)}下午2时53分\N三河郊外·食堂
